Love is not the absence of pain, but the choice to heal and forgive. It’s not the absence of flaws, but the choice to accept and embrace imperfections. Love is not the absence of disagreements, but the choice to communicate and find common ground. It’s not the absence of obstacles, but the choice to overcome and grow stronger together. Love is not the absence of fear, but the choice to trust and be vulnerable. It’s not the absence of differences, but the choice to respect and celebrate individuality. Love is not the absence of challenges, but the choice to persevere and support each other. Love is not the absence of darkness, but the choice to be guided by THE LIGHT for one another. It’s not the absence of selflessness, but the choice to prioritize the happiness and well-being of the other person. Love is not the absence of effort, but the choice to continuously nurture and invest in the relationship. Love is not the absence of anything, but the choice to actively choose love every single day. Happy Anniversary @stephbee__ 🎊💙🙏🏾💙🫶🏾🙏🏾💙🎊

Grateful to have experienced the magic of the Black Tie Cinematic Symphony at Kings Theatre. Sharing a space with these incredible human beings was a true honor. From reconnecting with old friends to meeting new ones, the night was filled with joy and laughter. @darwinhobbs brought Luther Vandross back TO LIFE.. Brittany Stewart exuded pure anointing. Donald Lawrence's musical genius left us in awe, and Iyanla's inspiring words uplifted our spirits. @yolandaadams is just special and finally, Dr. AR Bernard, the goat, capped off the night with a powerful message. This experience will forever be etched in my heart. 🎵✨congratulations @iamleonlacey the night was a huge success!! #BlackTieCinematicSymphony #KingsTheatre #IncredibleHumanBeings #SoulfulNight #MusicalGenius #InspirationOverflow #UnforgettableExperience
